Package: aRima.helper
Title: Make ARIMA modeling easier through interactive user interface
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kevin",
           family = "Craig",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kacraig@ncsu.edu")
Description: Simplifies ARIMA modeling by providing user interface and immediate results. 
    User can specify non-seasonal and or/seasonal AR, MA, and difference terms as well as dummy & Fourier terms. 
    Stationarity test, model convergence, fit statistics, ACF & PACF plots, residual plots, and white noise plots all provided.
    This package heavily uses the 'forecast' package by Rob Hyndman.
